<br>
Clue 1:<br>
She was a druid or a ranger - you could tell that by the buffs she cast on herself.  <br>
<br>
Clue 2:<br>
She was implemented on one the first days that the epics started going in.<br>
<br>
From there, we had already known that &quot;corruption&quot; had something to do with the epic - so people literally stood in front of her trying key words - Innoruuk, corruption, Venril Sathir.  Eventually it worked :P<br>
<br>
